Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Cook the chicken and pasta.', '2. Put the cooked chicken and pasta on a plate.']

behavior cook_chicken(chicken:item, pot:item, stove:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(chicken, pot) 
        # Place the chicken inside the pot

        achieve on(pot, stove) 
        # Ensure the pot with chicken is on the stove

        achieve is_on(stove) 
        # Turn on the stove to cook the chicken

behavior cook_pasta(pasta:item, pot:item, stove:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(pasta, pot) 
        # Place the pasta inside the pot

        if not has_water(pot):
            achieve has_water(pot) 
            # Make sure the pot has water for cooking pasta

        achieve on(pot, stove) 
        # Ensure the pot with pasta is on the stove

        achieve is_on(stove) 
        # Turn on the stove to cook the pasta

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        # Select the chicken item

        bind pasta: item where:
            is_dry_pasta(pasta)
        # Select the pasta item

        bind pot: item where:
            is_pot(pot)
        # Select a pot for cooking

        bind stove: item where:
            is_stove(stove)
        # Select a stove for cooking
        
        cook_chicken(chicken, pot, stove)
        # Cook the chicken

        cook_pasta(pasta, pot, stove)
        # Cook the pasta

        achieve close(faucet, pot)

        # Turn off the faucet after filling the pot

        # Place the pot back on the stove

        # Ensure the stove is on to continue cooking
